OL,3,CHome Office unaware how many migrants
OL,4,Chave overstayed skilled visas, MPs say
OL,6,FThe government has failed to gather
OL,7,F"basic information" such as whether
OL,8,Fpeople leave the UK after their visas
OL,9,Fexpire or how many might have stayed
OL,10,Fto work illegally, a cross-party
OL,11,Fcommittee of MPs has said.
OL,13,FThe Public Accounts Committee (PAC),
OL,14,Fwhich examines the value for money of
OL,15,Fgovernment projects, said the Home
OL,16,FOffice had not analysed exit checks
OL,17,Fsince the skilled worker visa route
OL,18,Fwas introduced in 2020 under the
OL,19,FConservatives.
