OL,6,FBut the MPs said there is both a lack
OL,7,Fof knowledge about what people do when
OL,8,Ftheir visas expire, and that the
OL,9,Fexpansion of the route in 2022 to
OL,10,Fattract staff for the struggling
OL,11,Fsocial care sector led to the
OL,12,Fexploitation of some migrant workers.
OL,14,FIts report said there was "widespread
OL,15,Fevidence of workers suffering debt
OL,16,Fbondage, working excessive hours and
OL,17,Fexploitative conditions", but adds
OL,18,Fthere is "no reliable data on the
OL,19,Fextent of abuses".
