OL,6,FIt noted that the fact a person's
OL,7,Fright to remain in the UK is dependent
OL,8,Fon their employer under the
OL,9,Fsponsorship model means migrant
OL,10,Fworkers are "vulnerable to
OL,11,Fexploitation".
