OL,6,FThe Home Office said more than 470
OL,7,Fsponsor licences in the care sector
OL,8,Fhad been revoked between July 2022 and
OL,9,FDecember 2024 in a crackdown on abuse
OL,10,Fand exploitation.
OL,12,FMore than 39,000 workers were
OL,13,Fassociated with those sponsors since
OL,14,FOctober 2020, the department said.
