OL,6,FCooper said the Labour government is
OL,7,Fbringing in e-visas to tackle the
OL,8,F"misuse and abuse of the visa system".
OL,10,FShe said under the previous
OL,11,Fgovernment, "we saw a big increase in
OL,12,Fthe number of visas, and yet no proper
OL,13,Fchecks and systems in place".
OL,15,F"We're reducing the number of visas
OL,16,Fissued, we are bringing in stronger
OL,17,Fcontrols, and we're also bringing in a
OL,18,Fmuch stronger digital system that will
OL,19,Fmean we can properly track entry and
OL,20,Fexit with digital e-visas as well,"
OL,21,Fshe said.
