OL,6,FIt also noted a lack of information
OL,7,Fabout what happens to people when
OL,8,Ftheir visas expire, stating that the
OL,9,FHome Office had said the only way it
OL,10,Fcan tell if people are still in the
OL,11,Fcountry is to match its own data with
OL,12,Fairline passenger information.
OL,14,FThe report said: "The Home Office has
OL,15,Fnot analysed exit checks since the
OL,16,Froute was introduced and does not know
OL,17,Fwhat proportion of people return to
OL,18,Ftheir home country after their visa
OL,19,Fhas expired, and how many may be
OL,20,Fworking illegally in the United
OL,21,FKingdom."
